# =============================================================================
# APPLICATION CODE (Auto-merge when CI passes)
# =============================================================================
#
# The following paths are NOT listed here intentionally to allow auto-merge:
#
# /src/                    - All Python source code
# /tests/                  - All test files  
# /config*.yaml            - Configuration files (validated by CI)
# /docs/                   - Documentation updates
# /requirements.txt        - Dependencies (security scanned by CI)
# /pyproject.toml          - Build configuration
# /.env.example            - Environment templates
# /README.md               - General documentation
# /notebooks/              - Jupyter notebooks
# /data/                   - Data files
# /legacy/                 - Legacy/archived code
#
# By NOT listing most files here, we enable auto-merge for source code,
# configs, documentation, and dependencies when CI validation passes.

